This is a World App miniapp project using:
- MiniKit SDK for World App integration
- World ID for human verification
- World Chain for blockchain interactions
- TypeScript/React for frontend
- Next.js API routes for backend

Key patterns:
- Always check MiniKit.isInstalled() before SDK calls
- Use verification_level: VerificationLevel.Orb for highest security
- Handle nullifier hashes for sybil resistance
- Use World Chain (Chain ID 480/4801) for transactions
- Follow mobile-first design principles

Reference official docs: docs.world.org/mini-apps